  {
    "id": "44924f25-cbde-4656-95d8-09271c9e9991",
    "sentence": "In the March 2021 SEP, no Committee member expected inflation to be over 3 percent for 2021. As I argued in a speech last December, this view was consistent with private-sector economic forecasts.",
