    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "ece1147f-2b77-4741-95f8-2c9930d31295",
    "sentence": "Making that judgment represents an important, but difficult task for policymakers.",
    "source": "The Federal Funds Rate in Extraordinary Times",
