    "con": "",
    "dom": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "02b796aa-fba7-4846-b2b4-350c0323b020",
    "sentence": "However, such a reduced-form description of the Committee's behavior does not answer the question of why this kind of inertia might be optimal.",
    "source": "Challenges for Monetary Policy Communication",
    "doc_type": "speech",
    "date": "2014-05-06",
