    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "b2f4658b-a8c2-4f0b-b882-bdf34518c836",
    "sentence": "Financial Regulation and Corporate Governance\r\n In the wake of the financial crisis, the public interest in regulation of banks and other financial firms is, I think it fair to say, both self-evident and substantial.",
    "source": "Corporate Governance and Prudential Regulation",
    "doc_type": "speech",
