  {
    "id": "754a8a8b-5ebc-47d1-9b8b-568c455b2c5f",
    "sentence": "While I expect inflation to eventually settle near our 2 percent target because of our policy actions, we have to make sure what we saw in yesterday's inflation report feeds through broadly across goods and services and that we do not revert back to what has been persistently high core inflation.",
    "source": "Big Shocks Travel Fast: Why Policy Lags May Be Shorter Than You Think",
    "doc_type": "speech",
